lass=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104luo1665702798079.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/luo1665702798079.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/luo1665702798079.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"luo1665702798079\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Field Syntax Library \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use this editor to model a reusable value for the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field Syntax</span> property, which determines the format for data entered in the field.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"luo1665702798079__p_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1\">At runtime, the syntax is checked, and some changes may be automatically applied, to ensure that it complies with the specified format.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"luo1665702798079__section_cwc_sv3_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d277231e61\">Properties</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"luo1665702798079__ul_yxr_sv3_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2279e1_d2280e1_d2281e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2282e1_d2283e1_d2284e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2285e1_d2286e1_d2287e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vzd1665702584055.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vzd1665702584055.html\" title=\"Specify a regex string or a syntax string to define the entry format of the data entered into the field at run time.\">Entry Format</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2288e1_d2289e1_d2290e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iun1665702712476.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iun1665702712476.html\" title=\"Specify whether a user can edit the data in the field. Default is True.\">Edit</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2291e1_d2292e1_d2293e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"okr1665702712545.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/okr1665702712545.html\" title=\"Specify whether the data in the field should be displayed. Default is True.\">Display</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2294e1_d2295e1_d2296e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sor1665702604768.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sor1665702604768.html\" title=\"Specify whether the field is included in the prompting sequence. Default is True.\">Prompt</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2297e1_d2298e1_d2299e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aml1665702712619.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aml1665702712619.html\" title=\"Specify whether the field is available to the user. Default is False.\">Dimmed</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2300e1_d2301e1_d2302e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wvk1665702676293.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wvk1665702676293.html\" title=\"Specify whether alphanumeric characters in this field are converted to uppercase as the user enters or leaves it.\">Uppercase</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2303e1_d2304e1_d2305e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mqc1665702676223.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mqc1665702676223.html\" title=\"Specify whether alphanumeric characters in this field are converted to lowercase as the user enters it or leaves the field.\">Lowercase</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tqh1665702712691.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tqh1665702712691.html\" title=\"Specify whether the field is mandatory.\">Mandatory</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2309e1_d2310e1_d2311e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gkb1665702712761.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gkb1665702712761.html\" title=\"Specify whether data is entered in this field in Overstrike or Insert mode. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Overstrike</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2312e1_d2313e1_d2314e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tsf1665702712830.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tsf1665702712830.html\" title=\"Specify whether the cursor automatically jumps to the next field in the prompt sequence when the maximum field length is reached. The default is False.\">Auto Jump</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2315e1_d2316e1_d2317e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"irh1665702712898.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/irh1665702712898.html\" title=\"Minimum number of characters allowed for data in this field.\">Minimum Field Length</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2318e1_d2319e1_d2320e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"azy1665702712971.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/azy1665702712971.html\" title=\"The maximum number of characters allowed for data in this field.\">Maximum Field Length</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2321e1_d2322e1_d2323e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fpw1665702713052.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpw1665702713052.html\" title=\"Characters that can be used in the field.\">Characters Allowed</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"luo1665702798079__li_d2324e1_d2325e1_d2326e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"anu1665702713194.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/anu1665702713194.html\" title=\"Use the language-specific input mode in the Input Method Editor.\">Use IME for input</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"luo1665702798079__section_jcx_tv3_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d277231e231\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"luo1665702798079__p_d7784e1_d7785e1_d7786e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lhc1704371292385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lhc1704371292385.html\" title=\"Create modeled properties using editors available on the More Editors menu. Use a modeled property by clicking the More icon ( icon ) in the appropriate property of an entity or field.\">Working with Modeled Properties</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zlt1665702557043.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Field Syntax</a><p>The Field Syntax property specifies the input format for data, including the entry format (for example, 1-Dec-14 or 20141201), the allowed characters, and whether the field is mandatory or read-only.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529742\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529742\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Field Syntax Library Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Field Syntax Library Use this editor to model a reusable value for the Field Syntax property, which determines the format for data entered in the field. At runtime, the syntax is checked, and some changes may be automatically applied, to ensure that it complies with the specified format. Properties Name Description Entry Format Edit Display Prompt Dimmed Uppercase Lowercase Mandatory Overstrike Auto Jump Minimum Field Length Maximum Field Length Characters Allowed Use IME for input How to Working with Modeled Properties Related Links Field Syntax The Field Syntax property specifies the input format for data, including the entry format (for example, 1-Dec-14 or 20141201), the allowed characters, and whether the field is mandatory or read-only. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}